<a href="/internships" style="color:#FFFFFF;"><img src="../../images/gi_intern.png"></a>    
</div>

<div style="width:21%; height:65%; float:left;border-left:1px dotted #666666;padding-left:15px;"><span class="greenboxheader">Fellowships</span>
	<p>Looking for an opportunity to be involved in <span class="bold">education research</span>? Givology fellows travel to rural villages and other sites abroad to conduct research on rural education, assist our field partners, and visit our sponsored projects and students. </p>
